Package nist.model

Class Category

java.lang.Object
nist.model.Category
public class Category extends Object
Represents a Category in the NIST data feed. A category groups vulnerabilities (CVEs) based on shared characteristics. Each category contains multiple vulnerability entries and various metrics.

This class includes summary information, statistical measures, and support for health-critical vulnerability tracking.
